Functional requirements:
•	Search (by departments and professors);
•	Login the user;
•	Register the user;
•	Rate the professor,
•	Show the info about each professor, any kind of rating


Feature list:
•	Like;
•	Tweet;
•	Comment;
•	Rate the professor from another university/school;
•	Ans from the professor

Not doing list:
•	Search by the rating;
•	The map of Kyrgyzstan with all schools and universities

User stories:
•	Simple user, who can view everything but can’t rate;
•	The registered user who is Simple user + can rate + comment
